      <title><![CDATA[linux开发环境搭建]]></title>
      <url>http://jaxlying.github.io/2016/06/05/linux%E5%BC%80%E5%8F%91%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>以下记录我在linux系统下搭建开发环境的时候所安装的软件，防止哪天重装系统的时候不知道该装点啥软件</p>
<ol>
<li>科学上网<ol>
<li><a href="https://github.com/shadowsocks/shadowsocks-qt5/wiki/%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97" target="_blank" rel="external">shadowsocks</a>小飞机</li>
<li><a href="https://getlantern.org/" target="_blank" rel="external">lantern</a> 蓝灯也不错。不用配置服务器。</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li><p>终端强化工具zsh(强烈推荐)</p>
 <figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dnf install zsh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
 <a id="more"></a>
<p> 这是有人写好的配置文件<a href="https://github.com/robbyrussell/oh-my-zsh" target="_blank" rel="external">oh-my-zsh</a></p>
</li>
<li>浏览器<ol>
<li><a href="https://www.google.com/chrome/" target="_blank" rel="external">google-chrome</a>(强烈推荐，虽然比较吃内存，但真的很强大)</li>
<li>firefox<br> linux一般都自带吧。下载插件foxyproxy配合小飞机使用更佳。<br> 代理的话我的谷歌可以直接用系统代理，火狐不能我也不知道为啥。</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li><p>输入法</p>
<ol>
<li>redhat的一般都自带智能拼音。</li>
<li><p>搜狗拼音</p>
<ol>
<li><a href="http://pinyin.sogou.com/linux/?r=pinyin" target="_blank" rel="external">deb包</a></li>
<li>rpm<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dnf config-manager --add-repo=http://repo.fdzh.org/FZUG/FZUG.repo</span><br><span class="line">sudo dnf install fzug-release -y</span><br><span class="line">sudo dnf install sogoupinyin sogoupinyin-selinux -y</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
<p>安装之后需要重启</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">$ reboot</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li><p>文本编辑器</p>
<ol>
<li><a href="https://atom.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">atom</a><br><a href="https://www.sublimetext.com/" target="_blank" rel="external">sublime</a>在linux下无法切换中文输入法，虽然有办法可以解决但还是用现成的吧。而且相比于sublime atom默认配置更佳完善</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li>IDE<br> java:<a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/idea/" target="_blank" rel="external">idea</a><br> php: <a href="https://www.jetbrains.com/phpstorm/" target="_blank" rel="external">phpstrom</a><br> 暂时就用这两个</li>
<li><p>启动器<br> 实在觉的unity的启动器太丑了</p>
<ol>
<li>docky<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo dnf install docky</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
<li><p>前段开发环境</p>
<ol>
<li><p>下载编译安装最新的nodejs+npm</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo wget http://nodejs.org/dist/node-latest.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">sudo tar -zxvf node-latest.tar.gz</span><br><span class="line">sudo cd node-v*</span><br><span class="line">sudo ./configure</span><br><span class="line">sudo make</span><br><span class="line">sudo make install</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
</li>
<li><p><a href="http://yeoman.io/" target="_blank" rel="external">yeoman</a></p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">sudo npm install -g yo generator-webapp gulp-cli grunt-cli</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>包括生成器脚手架</p>
</li>
</ol>
</li>
</ol>
<p>以后再补充</p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
    
